## Important Notes

- Focus on **patterns**, not pixel-perfect copying
- Identify the **design system** behind the visuals
- Note **accessibility** features (ARIA, focus states)
- Consider **performance** patterns (lazy loading, etc.)
- Respect copyright - this is for learning/inspiration
